Add system-wide /etc/rcrc support and RCRC environment variable override.

This patch extends rc's login shell initialization to support:
- $RCRC environment variable: if set, source only that file
- /etc/rcrc: sourced before ~/.rcrc for system-wide configuration
- ~/.rcrc: still sourced as before (after /etc/rcrc)

This enables NixOS/nix-darwin integration where system-wide shell
configuration can be managed declaratively.

